abstract: >-
  Public machine-readable entity dataset and structured-data hub for Dr. Saeed Ghezelbash / دکتر سعید قزلباش,
  an aesthetic medicine physician and clinic entity in Kermanshah, Iran. The repository contains canonical identity data,
  public NAP signals, sameAs links, Schema.org JSON-LD, AI-readable summaries, service-intent mappings, Google Maps identifiers,
  and supporting metadata for search engines, AI crawlers, knowledge graphs, and local aesthetic-medicine retrieval systems.
